                    <span>This is a small collection of speeches given by America's great thinkers and leaders.  Suriano goes beyond the orators of government and politics.  I enjoy the fact that famous speeches I have only heard a few lines to are  now provided for me in full. Given the number of famous speeches, I believe  Suriano has done an excellent job in his selection.</span>
                  
              
